Five minutes after checking in, we check right back out again, and high tail it over to the [Old Lion Apartments](http://www.oztravel.com.au/travel_mall/hotels/Old_Lion_ApartmNorth_A.html), which is where we stayed last time we were were here. We're welcomed back like long lost friends. 
